content.title: Skylift Block
content.stories: A tracerecord on KSN-K exhibition in Semarang. We ate delicious foods and pouch inordinately. The term “skylift” was taken because we were holding the exhibition on a 4-stories hotel. We were still considering Der Clone as a thread. We was eager to win the KSN-N, and to enroll in Universitas Indonesia; later we realized that our passion is not in the physic subject, though we seemed to be excel at. These songs are the very first songs after 2019/2020 new year transition. [docs-911]

content.title: Imaginary Block
content.stories: This tracerecord was made on behalf of Covid-19 disease. We, das Andante, were going back home until unspecified time. We rode our bike around Purwokerto city almost every day from 5.30 a.m. ‘till 7.30 a.m; inspired by our brother. We also went to Ribka’s house –a few days before we should return back to Salatiga—, observing her mid-open fence. This tracerecord was made purposely. We utilized a swimming google as a “flashback glass”. The tracerecord was the sequential of the Founder Block, as we were regretting Ribka and Bima’s engagement ... one year after we have established a self-reliant life in Salatiga. Our first Xiaomi phone ... bought, not gifted. [docs-911]

content.title: Complementary Block
content.stories: A complementary tracerecord of the Imaginary Block. Beside we were regretting Ribka, we also registered to a Poem Writing Competition, hoping that we can impress Ribka someday. Consider a parking staff on Pasar Wage that we considered as an ENFP; the first time we realized that our father is an ENFP; mom, an ISFJ; and our brother, an ESFP. The first time we followed C. S. Joseph in order to understand our type (we mistyped ourself as an INFP!), and the last time we owned an Instagram account. A transition between Ribka’s lust and Die Vintage’s realization of an INFJ –a “perfect” personality, that we had attempted to be one while riding our bike at 7 p.m. around the residence ... but failed. [docs-911]

This song was played over and over before the graduation day of Laques (Belly, Jacob, and Eli) and before the Stoney-Archer Consilience, when we played the song "Shelter" by Porter Robinson & Madeon using violins with Alley (and that's how we got the block name "Archer"). Memorable events during the tracing? Spending 2-3 hours every night with Alley watching "Let's Game It Out" and did other things as well, such as javelinizing Logbook and TOC while listening to this Block. [2022-02-06]

content.title: Forgive Block
content.stories: It was played during the very first 3 weeks of our "exhibition" at Rese/Suburban. We walked for 30 minutes to Rese every morning on weekdays while carrying an orange (broken) umbrella. We visited Etha for Sunday Service for four consequtive weeks, then on the 4th week, we visited Jci. It was warm and relieving to see Joan again (and to be hugged by her). Then we had a lunch together with Arpam at Ujo. We reconciliated with this city, Citizen. We worked on the Grand System (and we did!). We started writing Writers in other non-Foci branches, almost every night, at Sunne-G-B-D, sometimes after watching a video about mathematics on 3Blue1Brown y-Zedi. . And, most importantly, This was the first TR-B we listened to after **The Last Impression of "A" Consilience**. We forgave her, and we let her go. [2022-02-21]

content.title: Jarinet Block
content.stories: The TR we listened to during the Covid pandemic break in Citizen, that we had to go to Curle on weekdays to finish Aduta's because Suburban ordered all the students to study at home and not to come to Rese. Also, Unterbang played a whole bunch of movie review on y-Zedi, such as "Jari Netizen" (that's where the TR-I came from) at Sunne-FF. I occasionally listened to and watched it with him. [2022-03-21]

content.title: Granny Block
content.stories: The third Block traced in Sunne during Operation Voyage. This Block complements the previous "All Everything I Have (EIH) ..." series, - EIH II  --> Forgive Block; - EIH III --> Jarinet Block; - EIH I   --> Granny Block. We visited En's house in AABF during a one-week off-days due to Easter. (That's how we got the Block's Identity, "grandma/nenek".) This Block played during late Apollo VII and early Apollo VIII. Some notable experiences including the establishment of Kalo-FTJOT for Apollo, Apollo 7.2's Yokut Chromosome, and the attempts made to institutionalize Aefilum throughout Project Apollo 7.1. [2022-04-29]

content.title: Joana Block
content.stories: The tracerecord we listened to and started tracing the night before the graduation day of Suburban on June 24th, 2022, where we read a self-made poem "Second Life" in front of the students, parents, and supervisors during graduates performace.  During the tracing, we attended and ASH-ed the FLA CM 2022 of Jci on June 27-29. We became a photographer on the second and the third day of the event, using Nikon's DSLR camera as an aid. In that event, we also met Joan and encountered certain meaningful occurences, such as being at the Jci-FO together in one room. And that is how we came up with the TR-I "Joana". [2022-07-09]

content.title: Move Block
content.stories: The tracerecord that was listened to by TOSA during the state change period of Bewilderment IV and Neptunal V. It was traced before, during, and after the moving of B.A.S.E from Googleplex to Symbian (hence the identity "Move"). This TR-A became the first TR-A traced after the formalization of TR-B tracing (TR-B-Trac) as an Osteoloci (defined in Viruologe No. 44) that can only be done by a Topsider. [2022-10-05]

content.title: Zedist Block
content.stories: The very first TR-B that paved the way of utilizing Zedi in the tracing process. The TR-B was traced in Zedi in order to de-pirating Synthesia while avoiding having to listen to less-familiar and less-preferred free-to-download stock musics. It was traced on the first month of the Bewilderment IV period at Symbian. [2022-11-07]

content.title: Reminiscence Block
content.stories: The songs got us in time of the emergence of the non-Mirror-COA BSO Voyage III, a BSO on the fourth Homeleft. The "Makmur Mandiri" bus fare, the C-Travelo planning in advance, the 4.0 GPA, the "rainbow satisfying bubble warp immitation" and the "magnetic sketcher" owned by Five and/or Cent.  It bears the identity "Reminsicence" because the tracing mostly took place in Pixel, and the BSO Voyage III occured almost a year and a half after the last time we (collectively) left Wonderland for Sunne on October 7th, 2021—long before the Unanimous-Unbris was even a thing, and we were still emotionally engaged with Alley. Thus, the TR is a reminiscence of the post-A-N period and the post-Homeleft Consilience event. [2022-12-29]

content.title: Change Block
content.stories: The Tracerecord that was traced during the pre-Homeleft period of the Ramadhan vacation of BF-Meh-2. Almost every day did we sleep on the desk (marked by the logging of Logbook No. 585). It was named such, "Change," because there were many STATE CHANGES occuring during the tracing period of this z-TR. To name a few: - The overworking of QRI-Meh-1 for 12 hours and a half - The "Sosialisasi LK" event of NV-Meh-14 at Geen from 4 p.m. until 9.30 p.m. on a Friday - Video-call (for the first time) through Meta-FB with Xexo at Symbian after the Jcis for two hours  During the tracing period of this z-TR, we also attempted to Bodon (to donate blood) when the Bodon event was held at Adver due to Easter weeks. Nevertheless, we did not make it through the screening test because our hemoglobin level was 0.1 less than required at the time. [2023-04-19]

content.title: Low Block
content.stories: This z-Tracerecord got its name since it was traced and TR-B-to-TR-A converted during a period in the Art Order of Projectile-ZZZ called the Artistic Relapse Period (`zzz.0:300$y`), which is deemed as one of the lowest phase recorded during the writing of Projectile-ZZZ. Some events recorded during the tracing of Low Block's TR-B are: - Over-excessive Binet (Swimming Pool Vento `zzz.0:397~113`) - The second Feruar to Jci during a Wedcis (Second Feruar Vento `zzz.0:420~120`) - TO and Fideweb, violation against Ursia Decision (Cognitive Dissonance Vento `zzz.0:424~122`) - Breaking-up with Haha/Meta-FB for 120 hours (Quiet Week Vento `zzz.0:429~124`)  The TR-B was called "Enduring Control". And the `nd-1004` form narrates the TR-B as follows:  "[The TR-B] began being traced during the Artistic Relapse Period (`zzz.0:300$y`) where Wonit lost control over several things in his life —and he must endure the last weeks of Neptunal VIII" [2023-08-04]

content.title: Last Block
songs: Sketch 26 - A Galaxy Far Far Away
content.stories: The Tracerecord was traced during the restless period of Artistic Pitfall Loop (zzz.0:535), which was signified by the ever-increasing and climaxing intensity of zre-Ach-Fedor, Binet, Fideweb, TO-Fedor, and Fika. Eventually, this Tracerecord saw the eventual tragedy cascading from the Artistic Relapse Period (zzz.0:300) commonly known as the Wrecked Post-Artistic Loop (w.0:3) where Bear unattended any Neptunal X Sunsen Sudco Ulects for the entire 2 weeks since October 16th, 2023. [2023-10-30]  "It was traced following the climaxing and diminishing intensity of Artistic Relapse Period (zzz.0:300$y)" [/ssynthesia/spygrade/seahorse/nd/nd-1004/12-hopeful-recovery]

content.title: Guilt Block
songs: 旅列車 life train (travel train life train)
content.stories: This TR-A was traced during the second month of the ever-unveiling Qinxing (w.0:31$y) relapse of the Wrecked Post-Artistic Loop (w.0:3$y). During the tracing, gradually the stocks of milk powder, condiments, and other foods delivered from Map, Cent, and Dress, which were thought of to cause the urge to Binet, were depleted. Eventually, Powpow was no longer observed.  "It was traced during the beginning of the third week of the shameful (Culob-wise) occurrence of Wrecked Post-Artistic Loop (`w.0:3`) ... the "shameful destruction" of the Wrecked Post-Artistic Loop (w.0:3$y) created a sense of guilt within Wonit's self" [/ssynthesia/spygrade/seahorse/nd/nd-1004/13-shameful-destruction]

It was started being traced at the end of Sunsen's Neptunal X term, when consequences of Qinxing (`w.0:31$y`) started being felt by Wonit (II-φ). tr-data.title: Suspenzion Record
tr-data.desc:
This record was established during the period of Likikisit (`w.0:498~159`) in which period wonit had suspended from a significant number of Binary/Sunsen ulects. It was marked by the moving of B.A.S.E from Symbian to Kotilinit, which was believed to alleviate the malidarisit tendency of Four. The marking character "z" in "Suspenzion" was derived from "Halzion", which is one of the songs in the first TR-A of this record, Yue Block. This TR record also marked the beginning of bear's positive polarization toward Yue (`HWA 022-12 NC~120`)

Starting from this record, all YouTube playlists are given the corresponding description/story of TR-As.

content.title: Yue Block
content.stories: This TR-A marked wonit's increased positive polarization toward Yue as a Tisut. The story recounted in the poem **Yue Ponea** (`lp.0:310~120`) showed that once wonit had a scintillating conversation with Yue on a Saturday evening, and found out that Yue also had interests in Mili, Yorushika, and Toto. From Tuesday, July 30, 2024 to August 7, 2024, Bear and Yue continuously exchanged messages by means of Susunen. Therein Yue gave wonit several song recommendations by the artist "DAG", which wonit immediately listened to and made tracerecord. [2024-08-08]
